Amahigi Ni amagambo yifashishwaga n'abanyarwanda bakera, Bari guhiga [[inyamaswa]]. Aya magambo akaba yarari mu rujyano rwimvikana ko Ari indirimbo zo kubatera umurava, kugira ngo bataruha cg bakarambirwa Dore ko byabaga bitoroshye kubona inyamaswa ngo uyice. Bivugwa ko kurubu haruduce tumwe na tumwe nko muburengera zuba no mumajyaruguru hagikoreshwa amagorane ariko mu rwego rwo gususurutsa abana, nkibusakuzo cg mu bitaramo byumugoroba.
